{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1731039959.927128", "card_id": "Q_3494577200", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 154}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美联储继续宣布降息 25BP，这是美国近 4 年来的第二次降息，对全球经济将产生何种影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "北京时间 2024 年 11 月 8 日凌晨 3 点，美联储宣布降息 25 个 BP，将利率从 4.75%-5% 下调至 4.5%-4.75%。这是美国近 4 年来的第二次降息，距离今年 9 月降息 50BP 只隔了一个多月。 25BP！美联储年内第二次降息来了 - 21 经济网 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-fe78405c16e0386f04e49376c8998a95_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "693 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3494577200"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIoLD7853Sl+4SEAMaCTExMTY3NTY1NiCNorS5BjAAONcEQAByCjM0OTQ1NzcyMDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1731039959.928209", "card_id": "Q_3443156042", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 172}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪吒汽车启动大比例裁员，裁员比例最高或达到 70%， 背后原因有哪些？未来发展前景如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "财联社 11 月 7 日电，记者从多个独立信源处获悉，哪吒汽车今日启动大规模裁员。据内部人士透露，此次裁员比例最高或达到 70%。「正在分部门沟通，各部门有差异，总体比例没那么高。」另有哪吒汽车内部人士称。对此，哪吒汽车相关负责人向财联社记者确认公司正在进行组织架构调整，比例未知。10 月 29 日，哪吒汽车正式启动公司全员股权激励计划，同时宣布将实施机构精简、裁汰冗员、业务聚焦、扁平管理等一系列降本增效的举措。（财联社记者 徐昊）独家 | 哪吒汽车启动大比例裁员"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-62cc9bea63edfea11db967e2b58def41_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "522 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3443156042"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIoLD7853Sl+4SEAMaCTExMTY2NTM0NSCs47G5BjAAO